               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360613-name-524" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-524" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-524" type="surname" value="BURGESS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-524" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS BURGESS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an attorney, and live in York-street, Convent-garden. The prisoner was employed in my house as charwoman, in Fe<lb></lb>bruary and March, and until the 19th of May—I missed some silver spoons and spoke to her about them, on the 15th of May—she said she knew nothing about them, but probably they were in the room of a gentleman who lodged in my house—I went, and they were not there—I afterwards missed a table-cloth, and other linen, and told her of it—she said some had not come from the laundress, and some were not come from the mangle—she left on the 19th of May, without notice—I found her on the 28th at Bow-street-office.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360613-name-525" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-525" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-525" type="surname" value="ALLEN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-525" type="given" value="THOMAS WINDSOR"></interp>THOMAS WINDSOR ALLEN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am assistant to my father, a pawnbroker in Clare-street, Clare-market. I produce a shirt, a sheet, a towel, and other articles, which were pawned between March and May, by the pri<lb></lb>soner, for 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 7<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., together—they are worth about that—I do not think them worth 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.—we do not take things at their extreme value—we lend a fair price—more than half the value.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360613-name-526" type="witnessName">
