                  </hi>. I am shopman to Messrs. Lamb, of Stanhope-street, Clare-market—I produce some articles which were pawned by Mrs. Grady.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360613-name-527" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-527" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-527" type="surname" value="GRADY"></interp>
